---
title: Roasted Veggie Bengali Curry with Basmati Rice & Coriander
description: This delightful curry will knock your socks off with its easiness and tastiness. The Indian-inspired Bengal curry paste is a mild yet flavourful base of ginger, chilli, turmeric and fenugreek seeds, and it works perfectly with the roasted carrot and cauliflower to make a mouth-watering meal that's packed with veggie goodness.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65290344b776085eb7bd8afe-35a413c4.jpeg
